WEBVTT

00:14:29.773 --> 00:14:31.867
becomes, quickly,
kind of an absurd position

00:14:31.891 --> 00:14:36.955
where you can't say that,
objectively, ISIS's views are wrong.

00:14:36.979 --> 00:14:38.478
That's just their culture.

00:14:38.502 --> 00:14:41.699
We can't say they're wrong.
All we can do is fight them.

00:14:42.065 --> 00:14:44.121
