to plant a flag there,

00:14:44.145 --> 00:14:46.050
because you mentioned anthropology,

00:14:46.074 --> 00:14:51.138
which is a discipline which, 70 years ago,
in the aftermath of World War II,

00:14:51.162 --> 00:14:52.683
explicitly said,

00:14:52.707 --> 00:14:55.914
the American Anthropological
Association explicitly said,

00:14:55.938 --> 00:15:00.152
when the UN was trying to develop
a universal conception of human rights,